short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Estimate vehicle duty. Uses USD. It can be used on https://autocj.co.jp and https://www.beforward.jp.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension can be used to estimate the duty to be paid based on a vehicle's price(total Cost and Freight), year of make and engine capacity. It currently works in Malawi and uses US Dollars as the currency. It can be used on https://autocj.co.jp and https://www.beforward.jp. Developed by Madalitso Nyemba.
